    booklet provides some aids for printing simple booklets or signatures
for longer books.

Changes in version 0.7a (2005/06/01)
o Additional examples, no code changes

Changes in version 0.7 (2005/03/23)
o Cleaner interface with the memoir class

Changes (2004/04/16)
o Changed license from LPPL v1.0 to v1.3
o Updated contact details

Changes (2002/10/05)
o Expanded and improved documentation. No changes to any code.

Changes in version 0.6 of bkltprnt.sty (2001/08/26)
o Minimised the number of \box es

Changes in version 0.5 (2001/08/11)
o First public release

